data.title: White Fang
data.meta_description: WHITE  FANG - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document contains 20 multiple choice questions about the plot of Jack London's novel White Fang. The questions cover details like who wrote the novel, what kind of animal the main character is, how he came to join a sled dog team, encounters he has with humans and other dogs, and themes of the novel. Jack London is identified as the author of White Fang, which tells the story of a wolf-dog hybrid named White Fang and his journey to survival in the Yukon Territory.
